name: Live breeder information of: Rottie pups and German Shepherd pups
description:
Small breeder from the midwest.   Dedicated to the quality of health and temperament of her beloved favorite breeds.  German Shepherds and Rottweilers.  Est in 1992
Irish Eyes kennels aka "Donahue Dawgs" have joined together here, to advertise and promote these beautiful breeds.
OFA certified German Shepherds of Czech & E-Germ Working/Protection dogs.  And our lifelong certified therapy and family quality Rotts. LIVE ANIMALS WILL NOT BE SOLD FROM THIS SITE.  Only the products related to our dogs.
Shipping on live animals must be figured per airline, with added vet costs, create costs, and any other complying charges with shipping live animals.
CONTACT US on either of our web sites, below, for prices and availible pups.  We deal personally with our dogs and potential owners.   SERIOUS INQIERIES ABOUT THESE dogs/pups ONLY!
